                               SSC Site Status

   Stennis Space Center remains in a heightened security posture. Escorts
   will be required for all official visitors, vendors, and commercial
   deliveries. All through-site traffic and visitor center operations
   remain suspended. All SSC personnel should enter the gates at normal
   work times. For daily status reports, employees should call (228)
   688-3777 or check the NASA/SSC website at http://www.ssc.nasa.gov.
